track_notes: This is the G4ERP route. Park at SH82293926 just south of where C road crosses disused GWR line. Follow path parallel with line to 816390 and continue along farm track. At 815381 turn left and follow track uphill keeping wall then fence on your right. High on ridge cross to other side of fence at rusty old gate. Proceed along ridge to summit.

Descend from Moel Llyfnant to bwlch (a bit boggy). Ascend the other side, reaching stile at SH 82373545. Follow ridge line north. No cheating - nothing much is gained by trying to contour around the bumps. This took me 93 minutes.

Total time (including ops): 5hr 40m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T2. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
